    <item>
      <title>首席大法官罗伯茨表示人工智能将改变法院的工作方式</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-31/ai-and-the-supreme-court-justice-roberts-says-it-will-transform-judges-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首席大法官约翰·罗伯茨表示，人工智能将改变美国法院的运作方式，尽管人类法官还会出现“一段时间”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-31/ai-and-the-supreme-court-justice-roberts-says-it-will-transform-judges-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙推动经济“重整军备”以实现充分就业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-31/macron-pushes-for-economic-rearmament-to-reach-full-employment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙(Emmanuel Macron)因在2023年推动有时不受欢迎的改革而受到赞誉，并表示他将推动经济“重整军备”，力争在2027年实现充分就业的目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-31/macron-pushes-for-economic-rearmament-to-reach-full-employment</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 21:06:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿拉斯加附近货船上的锂离子电池火灾被扑灭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-31/lithium-ion-battery-fire-in-a-cargo-ship-s-hold-is-out-after-several-days-of-burning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉斯加州安克雷奇（美联社）一艘大型货船的锂离子电池在货舱中燃烧了几天后，美国海岸警卫队周六晚间表示，火势已被扑灭，并指示该船在阿拉斯加荷兰港附近抛锚。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2023-12-31/lithium-ion-battery-fire-in-a-cargo-ship-s-hold-is-out-after-several-days-of-burning</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Dec 2023 19:08:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西推出 40 亿美元激励措施的流动计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-31/brazil-launches-mobility-program-with-4-billion-in-incentives</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西政府发布了一项临时措施，为当地汽车行业制定新的指导方针，包括车队可持续性要求和新技术生产的激励措施。]]></description>
